<li><a href="http://www.dharmanet.com.br/multimidia/mp3.php" class="external text" title="http://www.dharmanet.com.br/multimidia/mp3.php" rel="nofollow">DharmaSound: Sūtra do Coração in various languages</a> (mp3)</li>
</ul>
